rows.label: tlk41700121_07_msg0001
rows.name:
Right now, the people of Trigo are
doing everything they can to get new
houses built for the refugees.

rows.label: tlk41700121_07_msg0002
rows.name:
After all, they can hardly live
in tents in the Superbian army
base forever.

rows.label: tlk41700121_07_msg0003
rows.name:
It's only natural that many of them are
depressed or angry. How can they feel
safe without a roof over their heads?
